 </property>
 </activation>
 <properties>

# Reasoning

The issue is asking to add a Maven profile to the `pom.xml` file to run the Quarkus native build. This profile will be activated when the `native` property is set, and it will set the `quarkus.package.type` property to `native` and `skipITs` to `false`.

To address this issue, we need to add the provided XML section to the `pom.xml` file. This section defines a new profile with the id `native` that will be activated when the `native` property is set. The profile sets two properties: `quarkus.package.type` to `native` and `skipITs` to `false`.
